---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section
  class="py-section-padding px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop relative overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-low"
>
  <div
    class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center bg-white rounded-[40px] border border-outline-variant p-12 md:p-20 relative shadow-2xl overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute -top-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-background border-4 border-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
    >
      <span
        class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl"
        style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">celebration</span
      >
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-56 h-56 hidden lg:block hover:scale-110 transition-transform pointer-events-none"
    >
      <img
        alt="Pulsi Mascot Demo"
        class="w-full h-full object-contain"
        src={`${base}images/solicitar_demo.png`}
      />
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-headline-xl text-headline-xl mb-6">
      Empieza a entender lo que ocurre en tu organización
    </h2>
    <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10">
      Únete a los líderes que están transformando la cultura de sus equipos con evidencia real y
      humana.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <button
        class="primary-gradient text-on-primary font-label-md text-label-md font-bold px-10 py-5 rounded-full shadow-2xl shadow-primary/40 hover:scale-105 transition-all"
      >
        Solicitar Demo Personalizada
      </button>
      <p class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">
        Sin compromisos • Configuración en 5 min
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
